msgctxt "mn147:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 147 "
msgstr "Middle Discourses 147 "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn147:0.2"
msgid "Cūḷarāhulovādasutta "
msgstr "The Shorter Advice to Rāhula "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: nya1, pts-vp-pli3.278, sc1
msgctxt "mn147:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "mn147:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavato rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi: "
msgstr "Then as he was in private retreat this thought came to his mind, "

msgctxt "mn147:1.4"
msgid "“paripakkā kho rāhulassa vimuttiparipācanīyā dhammā. "
msgstr "“The qualities that ripen in freedom have ripened in Rāhula. "

msgctxt "mn147:1.5"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ rāhulaṃ uttariṃ āsavānaṃ khaye vineyyan”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I lead him further to the ending of defilements?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:1.6"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, entered Sāvatthī for alms. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:1.7"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then, after the meal, on his return from alms-round, he addressed Venerable Rāhula, "

msgctxt "mn147:1.8"
msgid "“gaṇhāhi, rāhula, nisīdanaṃ; "
msgstr "“Rāhula, get your sitting cloth. "

msgctxt "mn147:1.9"
msgid "yena andhavanaṃ tenupasaṅkamissāma divāvihārāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Let’s go to the Dark Forest for the day’s meditation.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:1.10"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā rāhulo bhagavato paṭissutvā nisīdanaṃ ādāya bhagavantaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandhi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” replied Rāhula. Taking his sitting cloth he followed behind the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya2, sc2
msgctxt "mn147:2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena anekāni devatāsahassāni bhagavantaṃ anubandhāni honti: "
msgstr "Now at that time many thousands of deities followed the Buddha, thinking, "

msgctxt "mn147:2.2"
msgid "“ajja bhagavā āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ uttariṃ āsavānaṃ khaye vinessatī”ti. "
msgstr "“Today the Buddha will lead Rāhula further to the ending of defilements!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:2.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle paññatte āsane nisīdi. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha plunged deep into the Dark Forest and sat at the root of a tree on the seat spread out. "

msgctxt "mn147:2.4"
msgid "Āyasmāpi kho rāhulo bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "Rāhula bowed to the Buddha and sat down to one side. "

msgctxt "mn147:2.5"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.279, sc3
msgctxt "mn147:2.6"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, rāhula, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Rāhula? "

msgctxt "mn147:2.7"
msgid "cakkhu niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "Is the eye permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:2.8"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:2.9"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti? "
