msgctxt "mn147:9.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmiṃ nibbindati, rūpesu nibbindati, cakkhuviññāṇe nibbindati, cakkhusamphasse nibbindati, yamidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact. And they grow disillusioned with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness that arises conditioned by eye contact. "

msgctxt "mn147:9.2"
msgid "Sotasmiṃ nibbindati, saddesu nibbindati … pe … "
msgstr "They grow disillusioned with the ear … "

msgctxt "mn147:9.3"
msgid "ghānasmiṃ nibbindati, gandhesu nibbindati … "
msgstr "nose … "

msgctxt "mn147:9.4"
msgid "jivhāya nibbindati, rasesu nibbindati … "
msgstr "tongue … "

msgctxt "mn147:9.5"
msgid "kāyasmiṃ nibbindati, phoṭṭhabbesu nibbindati … "
msgstr "body … "

msgctxt "mn147:9.6"
msgid "manasmiṃ nibbindati, dhammesu nibbindati, manoviññāṇe nibbindati, manosamphasse nibbindati, yamidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, and mind contact. And they grow disillusioned with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness that arises conditioned by mind contact. "

msgctxt "mn147:9.7"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati, virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:9.8"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "mn147:9.9"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn147:9.10"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā rāhulo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Rāhula was happy with what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn147:9.11"
msgid "Imasmiñca pana veyyākaraṇasmiṃ bhaññamāne āyasmato rāhulassa anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucci. "
msgstr "And while this discourse was being spoken, Rāhula’s mind was freed from defilements by not grasping. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn147:9.12"
msgid "Tāsañca anekānaṃ devatāsahassānaṃ virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "And the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in those thousands of deities: "

msgctxt "mn147:9.13"
